Package uk.ac.ed.inf

Record Class Restaurant

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
uk.ac.ed.inf.Restaurant
Record Components:
name - the name of the Restaurant
lng - the longitude coordinate of the restaurant
lat - the latitude coordinate of the restaurant
menu - the items on the restaurant's menu
public record Restaurant(String name, double lng, double lat, List<Menu> menu) extends Record
This class is used to store details of each restaurant based on the information fetched from the REST Server.
